  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Participants will be randomized to undergo a High Tibial Osteotomy (HTO) with or without a
      knee scope. Patients will be tested in the Gait Lab, will fill out quality-of-life
      questionnaires, and have a clinical evaluation done preoperative and at each follow-up visit.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
